history.content: Please ask your ESS Advisor. Unit minimums/maximums are regulated by the Colleges.

I'll be a second semester senior in the Spring, and after this fall semester, I will have completed all of my EECS degree requirements. If I were also to be a 20 hour TA, how many units would I need to take in the spring? And would I need to take any of them for a letter grade?
history.subject: Unit minimum if all degree reqs completed
